<br>
If they did implement a change like that, I see them assuming the simple stance and simply allowing people to change their deities at will, once and once only.  Why go through the effort of designing a bazillion new quests when you can do it so easily...and the precident is already there with /facepick.<br>
<br>
Of course, there are also possible faction exploits to this...they'd have to not allow this change to affect the player's current faction lists.<br>
<br>
Shizz<br>
